## Typography

### Font Families
| Token | Font | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| `--font-sans` | Inter | UI text, labels, buttons, headings |
| `--font-mono` | JetBrains Mono | URLs, code, JSON, method badges, status codes, timestamps |

### Type Scale
| Size | Weight | Usage |
