### Architecture
```
GitHub Release (tag push)
  ↓
GitHub Actions: build + sign (Windows/macOS/Linux)
  ↓
Upload: binaries + signatures + latest.json
  ↓
User launches app
  ↓
useUpdateChecker() → check() on startup + 4h interval
